al failures in native tests, adding `org.h2.Driver` to the reflect-config could be wise.\\n\\n**Evaluating configuration settings**\\n\\nI’m looking at site line 299 and its records coverage in the JVM. I think it’s fine for native to use the configuration. However, I need to reflect the configuration in exact JSON format. That means I should make sure to append entries correctly. It's important that everything aligns perfectly to ensure it works as intended! Making sure I’m thorough here will help avoid any issues down the line.\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0e0eeea9a3b9577e0169f63ab2e2b881a38d5fe10437e806c9\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp9jq-P6Lau7UcCn4zGBU6ndyHqULgKEaXFoHoAPckn0MkX-n-vDOmjKeoENe3XpGlxOAQ1b5G-NVjgIVDuvIYFR6OTCFDqAp1Y3OaKHj8ka7fpkDulaCTNU5l4dRUFgDWy1y8VBFAPeuruoX0sn4QQ3b30q9sDrpNIys6uZlsMSoS6ipL9Coaoq7trflDY9KOC9NqZOJmKhwqD_nw8i1lq5LYb0eW6hLOwmh_gy7ZWXDnyibRrB4_ZtwuDixiJbZOzn-xqtrY8VhTYgc1cEf7X_TxoRMmAsFLAj1-60NUS6l06RcwaybC99Wwq-qm5YG6YKlGW5PGF4K5JK2JcSjKB1jKyx-D5k8BIP_FTtbVMJUbZmwgMdpRn5_G6fa-jlT9g0jOBvARhMNHpAYtFZfS3TzBvXfIzezoRUCnioHLNY2ERinuPxo_YO3wz25Xeuet3QEFAREZtxhFhz6_XMrByRfVNyGhW6XjSwax0amlLLb-YqgbwlgmFqaO7BW4pdkPZllHNeljHLmsBdwxdgXQ_80RitZigUvjfLKQ1reBjztS6FKEK-BRlKkDIFJsmK5XOrHkeU5aDnUsaTegfhhzNtNa53BK-KY31iJ68Z2RU8fyFkUFrYZiFVF_NnfFmLuld23fy-ycZ2rls-K-xF46IMyi0Mmsybyts88aamIgLWYaaNnTb_F3N6_Ui10pNarxNZMtaWUXxi8qvXOxDv2xO9HNJuZNBrdecWvmsv_X_Kszw-gs1FVQmgH-3JwVefjGGgZT2u1Z7efEbXib4td3usSdmZl0G8H57hbZD67vcnmMJ_CaGccznbUFmFgMQeE1YJkrtrxMaM9Bld0BQDmyoO-T1pTKAN658TxSI72xij9Fplc53BID-pyk4aWyoLm9xOOWgZnCwAezEvzqMJQ2D0Hdp5Mv8rKYOzjjJjMzFCm2yJZlmsjjomhaKvX1FRFodzfhideWoaiy9KdDKUM-X2mckqdAGd4oaeraW_r8oqpEKAR0PrqGs2u8FW5x6vxbVEy0GQEUaTdC1rOronJ3E_bvpDhLov4oIa_mBxJnehhk0IzuTPlxzCO04C-cPwEqs8SnBUQzieGFnhIPWVIpQUhaC9faVxYniRFLTwaWuEX9fvl1Q_db1MYpiZXwPrtV9B0bwIBKDJI2tDghUHtMToMs_rA2unH-TSawtxRoIn4aDYJ7bVBQ4EnMAWfXWraABCTZGz9dQdnhjACimyyildUrEbAe07lphfI7zOwQEISbvkqAfl34js2vJXrU8ZaP4GamnjENEsrJP